Package org.ietf.nea.pb.message.util

IETF TNCCS message supporting values.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PbMessageSubValue
    Generic value contained in a TNCCS message value as supporting value.
    PbMessageSubValueBuilder<T extends PbMessageSubValue>
    Generic builder base to build a supporting value for a TNCCS message value.
    PbMessageValueErrorParameterOffsetBuilder
    Generic builder to build a TNCCS message error parameter value with an error offset compliant to RFC 5793.
    PbMessageValueErrorParameterVersionBuilder
    Generic builder to build a TNCCS message version error parameter value compliant to RFC 5793.
    PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilder
    Generic builder to build a TNCCS message string remediation parameter value compliant to RFC 5793.
    PbMessageValueRemediationParameterUriBuilder
    Generic builder to build a TNCCS message URI remediation parameter value compliant to RFC 5793.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPbMessageValueErrorParameter
    Generic IETF RFC 5793 error parameter base.
    AbstractPbMessageValueRemediationParameter
    Generic IETF RFC 5793 remediation parameter base.
    PbMessageValueErrorParameterFactoryIetf
    Factory utility to create an IETF RFC 5793 compliant error parameter.
    PbMessageValueErrorParameterOffset
    IETF RFC 5793 TNCCS error parameter with offset.
    PbMessageValueErrorParameterOffsetBuilderIetf
    Builder to build a TNCCS message error parameter value with an error offset compliant to RFC 5793.
    PbMessageValueErrorParameterVersion
    IETF RFC 5793 TNCCS unsupported version error parameter.
    PbMessageValueErrorParameterVersionBuilderIetf
    Builder to build a TNCCS message version error parameter value compliant to RFC 5793.
    PbMessageValueRemediationParameterFactoryIetf
    Factory utility to create a IETF RFC 5793 compliant remediation parameter.
    PbMessageValueRemediationParameterString
    IETF RFC 5793 TNCCS string remediation parameter.
    PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilderIetf
    Builder to build a TNCCS message string remediation parameter value compliant to RFC 5793.
    PbMessageValueRemediationParameterUri
    IETF RFC 5793 TNCCS URI remediation parameter.
    PbMessageValueRemediationParameterUriBuilderIetf
    Builder to build a TNCCS message URI remediation parameter value compliant to RFC 5793.
